        <h3>Design</h3>
        <p class="project-font-grey">To ensure the project fitted seamlessly with other ABC kids apps, I was given access to a range of artwork created by ABC kids. I chose to design the app using a flashcard concept as it is a tried and tested learning technique that parents trust and children enjoy. To reinforce this concept I designed a card packet for each category. Each card within the category was also themed with with one particular ABC brand. For example the category ‘Food’ was themed with The Wiggles characters and artwork. The actual flashcard and their flipping animation was created using SCSS, with the relevant image and text placed within.</p>
